{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or when I was working on the [NON-ENGLISH], we would have-- we would save the inside bags of cement-- remove the outer and inner pieces of cement out of the paper.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were about four layers of paper that we saved and cut out a-- a neck, and wore sleeves, cut out sleeves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you wore it as a-- as a windbreak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- but we had-- we had good clothes accumulated through these-- we were there over a year.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think-- I don't remember how many, but I think there were, at the camp at that time, must have been over 10,000.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I think 5,000 went with us on this march.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The average person wore-- well, the uniform was you had underwear, and you had a-- a-- a jacket, and pants, a shirt, and an overcoat, all of-- made out of denim, made out of a very thin material.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not very-- not very warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had the number on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had two stars, two-- two triangles, a yellow and a red triangle superimposed on each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that made a star of David.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The yellow being Jews, and the red being political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, there was a P on it for-- for Pole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't have to have a P, we just had the-- the two triangles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were marched out quite quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think we must have gone about 20 kilometers in the first day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we could hear the-- the war coming closer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- you know, the shells were bursting in the air.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'd hear the Front not far from us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the people-- some people-- I had-- you know, some people were left in the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
